对于各变量的说明：

PassengerId:标识乘客的ID

Survived:（需要预测的变量）1代表存活，0为死亡

Pclass：客舱等级，1为高级，2为中级，3为低级

Name：乘客名字

Sex：乘客性别

Age：乘客年龄

SibSp：在船兄弟姐妹数/配偶数

Parch：在船父母数/子女数

Ticket：船票编号

Fare：船票价格

Cabin：客舱号 (缺失值较多)

Embarked：登船港口

2 变量提取

2.1 称谓提取

full$Title <- gsub("(.*, )|(\\..*)","",full$Name)  #提取名字中 逗号后面和点句号前面的字符，一般可能是Mr. Mrs这样的特殊称谓)


rare_title <- c('Dona','the Countess','Capt', 'Col', 'Don', 
                'Dr', 'Major', 'Rev','Jonkheer')  #出现较少的title
full$Title[full$Title == 'Lady']        <- 'Miss'
full$Title[full$Title == 'Mlle']        <- 'Miss' 
full$Title[full$Title == 'Ms']          <- 'Miss'
full$Title[full$Title == 'Mme']         <- 'Mrs'
full$Title[full$Title == 'Sir']         <- 'Mr'
full$Title[full$Title %in% rare_title]  <- 'Ow'

2.2 年龄提取

generate.new.feature.is.Young <- function(titanic.data)
{
  titanic.data$is.Young<-'Adult'
  titanic.data$is.Young[titanic.data$Age<=10]<- 'Child'
  titanic.data$is.Young[titanic.data$Age > 10 & titanic.data$Age < 30]<- 'Youth'
  titanic.data$is.Young[titanic.data$Age > 60]<- 'Aged'
  titanic.data$is.Young <- as.factor(titanic.data$is.Young)
  return(titanic.data)
}
full = generate.new.feature.is.Young(full)

2.3 家庭规模提取

generate.new.feature.family.size <- function(titanic.data)
{
  titanic.data$family.size <- titanic.data$Parch+titanic.data$SibSp+1
  return(titanic.data)
}
full = generate.new.feature.family.size(full)

  capture[i] <- capture[i-1] + capture[i]
}
capture <- capture / sum(data$Survival)
data_plot <- cbind(as.data.frame(coverage), as.data.frame(capture))
# 绘制覆盖率-捕获率曲线

# 九折交叉验证
set.seed(105)
n <- sample(1:889, 889)
group <- rep(1:9, each = 99)[1:889]
pred <- numeric(nrow(train_new))
for (i in 1 : 9){
  ii <- n[group == i] # 第i组的行号
  logit_model <- glm(Survival ~ ., family = binomial(link = "logit"), data = train[-ii, ]) # 对于每个组，用剩下的组做逻辑线性回归
  pred[ii] <- predict(logit_model, train[ii, ], type = "response") #根据每个回归的结果做预测
}
#as.data.frame(pred)
# 提取捕获率和覆盖率信息
pred <- as.data.frame(cbind(train$Survival == "Survived", pred))
names(pred) <- c("Survival",'Prob')
pred <- pred[order(-pred$Prob), ]
n <- nrow(pred)
coverage <- seq(1,n)
capture <- rep(0,n+1)
for (i in 2:(n+1)) {
  capture[i] <- capture[i-1] + pred[i-1,1]
}
capture <- capture[-1]
coverage <- coverage/n
capture <- capture/(nrow(pred[which(pred[1]==1),]))

4.2.3 提升树
# boosting模型
train_model <- adaboost(Survival ~.,data=train_new,nIter=100)  
boost.imp <- train_model$trees$`0`$variable.importance  
# boosting预测
a <- predict(train_model, newdata=test_new)
boost.table<- table(a$class,test_new$Survival)
boost.accuracy<-(sum(diag(boost.table)))/sum(boost.table)

4.2.4 变量重要性表格
#变量重要性表格
#boost.imp
variable <- data.frame(variable = c("Title", "Family size", "Pclass", "Age", "Embarked"), importance = unname(boost.imp))
variable[1:5,2] <- 100 * variable[1:5,2]/variable[1,2]
#variable[1,2] <- 1
#variable[1:9,2] <- 100 * variable[1:9,2]
p <- ggplot(variable,aes(variable,importance))+
  geom_bar(stat="identity",position="stack",alpha=1,fill = "darkturquoise")+ 
  labs(y="Variable importance")+
  theme(plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5,size = 20,colour = 'slategray4'))+ 
  scale_y_continuous(breaks=seq(0,100,20))+
  scale_x_discrete(limits= variable$variable)+coord_flip()+
  theme(axis.title.x=element_text(size=14,colour = 'slategray4'))+ theme(axis.title.y=element_blank())
p
